Greetings from Los Angeles and welcome back to In the Room, my private emai=
l on the media business. The top takeaway from a busy media earnings week i=
s that nearly every legacy mediaco=E2=80=94Disney, NBCUniversal, WBD, Param=
ount, etcetera=E2=80=94is now saying the quiet part out loud: Their TV news=
 businesses are in free fall. The silver lining: Their streaming businesses=
 are growing and, with the exception of Peacock, actually turning a profit.=
 The challenge, obviously, is figuring out how to grow these streaming busi=
nesses fast enough to outpace the decline on the linear side=E2=80=94that i=
s, if they can=E2=80=99t find a way to sell off or otherwise excise those l=
egacy assets. Good luck.

