 media business. The top takeaway from a busy media earnings week is that n=
early every legacy mediaco=E2=80=94Disney, NBCUniversal, WBD, Paramount, et=
cetera=E2=80=94is now saying the quiet part out loud: Their TV news busines=
ses are in free fall. The silver lining: Their streaming businesses are gro=
wing and, with the exception of Peacock, actually turning a profit. The cha=
llenge, obviously, is figuring out how to grow these streaming businesses f=
ast enough to outpace the decline on the linear side=E2=80=94that is, if th=
ey can=E2=80=99t find a way to sell off or otherwise excise those legacy as=
sets. Good luck.
